Name: Fox Girl Taming
About the game: This is a casual game that trains your spatial thinking ability. Massive levels, extremely difficult. In each level, push the cage to the position of the fox to lock up the fox, and lock up all the foxes in the cage to complete the task of the level. The more foxes you capture, the more likely you are to get a transformed fox girl.
